===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm}} < {{etyl|fro}} {{term|lang=fro|plait}}, {{term|lang=fro|plaid}} < {{etyl|ML.}} {{term|lang=la|placitum||a decree, sentece, suit, plea, etc., {{etyl|la}} an opinion, determination, prescription, order, lit. that which is pleasing, pleasure}}, neuter of {{term|lang=la|placitus}}, past participle of {{term|lang=la|placere||to please}}.

